BusinessTech has cemented its place as the biggest business news website in South Africa, reaching 8 million South African readers in May 2020. BusinessTech served 8.1 million unique South African browsers and 31.9 million page views during the month. These readership numbers are based on the latest report from Narratiive, the official traffic measurement partner of the IAB South Africa. What makes this figure impressive is the quality of this readership, which consists of business decision makers, C-level executives, senior managers and directors, and company owners. BusinessTech editor Gareth Vorster said their goal is to provide readers with trusted information which they can use to inform their personal and business decision making. “BusinessTech leads the way in accurate and up-to-the-minute news coverage, combined with in-depth data-driven journalism. This ensures that our readers remain up to date with the latest business content as the country navigates its way through the current recovery period,” said Vorster. BusinessTech’s high-quality audience consists of South African professionals, managers, business owners, and executives. Every month, millions of professionals read BusinessTech, including: 1.5 million managers
900,000 business owners
860,000 executives
118,000 CEOs and directors This sought-after audience has attracted many new advertisers to BusinessTech who are now using the platform to speak directly to business decision makers, and readers with high spending power in their personal capacity. The graphic below provides an overview of the BusinessTech monthly readership. <img class="wp-image-404175 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/BusinessTech-scaled.jpg" alt="BusinessTech" width="640" height="905" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/BusinessTech-scaled.jpg 1810w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/BusinessTech-212x300.jpg 212w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/BusinessTech-724x1024.jpg 724w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/BusinessTech-768x1086.jpg 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/BusinessTech-1086x1536.jpg 1086w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/BusinessTech-1448x2048.jpg 1448w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/BusinessTech-1200x1697.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> This article was published in partnership with BusinessTech.